responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "8BC0AF9B4ADCB5370E53EB8F404C52AC", "Before the Mother of Maidens did rest a magical pot and ornate treasure chest. Speaking aloud the pot did exclaim, \"Jump into the chest or death will you claim!\" Lifting the lid and peering into the abyss, she held fast because daughters she would miss. \"There is little time for sorrow. In we go or flat as a flapjack we be.\" Quickly she removed an necklace of hearts and laid it to rest as a gift if she did not return. With that, she was in and gone.")
name: MADD_0002_MOM_VuulVodex_31
